extends ../../../master-dashboard

block content
	div.mdl-cell.mdl-cell--12-col
		h2 Project Allotment

	div.mdl-cell.mdl-cell--12-col
		ul.mdl-list
			li.mdl-list__item.
				2016 batch students are eligible to choose only ONE project type course in this semester. 

			li.mdl-list__item.
				2015 batch DUAL DEGREE students are allowed to take ONE project type courses in this semester.

			li.mdl-list__item.
				2015 batch SINGLE DEGREE students are allowed to take TWO project type courses in this semester.

			li.mdl-list__item.
				2017 batch students are not allowed to take project-type courses.

			li.mdl-list__item
				span.mdl-list__item-primary-content
					i.material-icons.mdl-list__item-icon note
					| These courses will be available only to those students who have elective slot(s) in their prescribed semester wise chart for the semester and who are eligible to register in these courses as per Academic Regulations

			li.mdl-list__item
				span.mdl-list__item-primary-content
					i.material-icons.mdl-list__item-icon note
					| Students who want to propose their own project idea, can contact the concerned faculty member.					

	div.mdl-cell.mdl-cell--3-col.center
		button.mdl-button.mdl-js-button.mdl-button--raised.mdl-js-ripple-effect.mdl-button--primary(onclick="window.location.replace('#{rootURL}/#{reqPortal}/view')")
			i.material-icons add
			| View Projects

	div.mdl-cell.mdl-cell--3-col.center
		button.mdl-button.mdl-js-button.mdl-button--raised.mdl-js-ripple-effect.mdl-button--primary(onclick="window.location.replace('#{rootURL}/#{reqPortal}/update-info')")
			i.material-icons edit
			| Update Projects info			

	div.mdl-cell.mdl-cell--3-col.center
		button.mdl-button.mdl-js-button.mdl-button--raised.mdl-js-ripple-effect.mdl-button--primary(onclick="window.location.replace('#{rootURL}/#{reqPortal}/faq')")
			i.material-icons question_answer
			| FAQs

	div.mdl-cell.mdl-cell--3-col.center
		button.mdl-button.mdl-js-button.mdl-button--raised.mdl-js-ripple-effect.mdl-button--primary(onclick="window.location.replace('#{rootURL}/#{reqPortal}/manage')")
			i.material-icons settings
			| Application Status
